org.springframework.cloud.dataflow.core.dsl

Class LabelledTaskNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.cloud.dataflow.core.dsl.AstNode
      • org.springframework.cloud.dataflow.core.dsl.LabelledTaskNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FlowNode, SplitNode, TaskAppNode

    public abstract class LabelledTaskNode
extends AstNode
    The main task supertype AST node. Other nodes like FlowNode and SplitNode extend this one, relying on this one for common functionality.
    Author:
    Andy Clement
